{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/report-vat-fraud.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/report-vat-fraud","title":"Report VAT fraud","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:21:02+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2368","business_proposition":true,"description":"Reporting VAT fraud to HM Revenue & Customs anonymously ","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You can report someone to HM Revenue &amp; Customs (<abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>) if you think they’re committing <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> fraud - you don’t have to give your name.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can report <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://online.hmrc.gov.uk/shortforms/form/CusConf_InformB?dept-name=Customs&amp;sub-dept-name=Hotline&amp;location=48&amp;origin=http://www.hmrc.gov.uk\" title=\"Customs Hotline\"><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> fraud online</a> or by telephone. </p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Customs 24 hour hotline</strong><br />\n0800 595 000</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>For your own safety don&rsquo;t:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>try to find out more about the fraud</li>\n  <li>let anyone know you&rsquo;re reporting it</li>\n  <li>encourage anyone to commit a crime so you can get more information</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>What is <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> fraud?</h2>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> fraud is when a business doesn&rsquo;t charge <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> when they should, or charges you <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> but doesn&rsquo;t pay it to <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>. For example, they might:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>ask you to pay cash to avoid paying <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> on a sale or job</li>\n  <li>not be registered for <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> when they should be</li>\n  <li>use a <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> number that&rsquo;s false or belongs to someone else</li>\n  <li>claim to have applied for a <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> number when they haven&rsquo;t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You can <a href=\"http://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/vies/vatRequest.html\" title=\"VIES VAT number validation\" rel=\"external\">check a UK <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> number is valid.</a></p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"short_description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"VAT","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax%2Fvat.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes online returns, rates, charging and record keeping","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=tax%2Fvat","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax/vat"},"parent":{"title":"Money and tax","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes VAT, debt and inheritance tax","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=tax","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax"},"parent":null}}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/report-cash-in-hand-pay.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/report-cash-in-hand-pay","title":"Report cash in hand pay","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:22:51+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/report-an-unregistered-trader-or-business.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/report-an-unregistered-trader-or-business","title":"Report a trader or business for tax evasion","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-12-04T14:10:17+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/report-tobacco-or-alcohol-tax-evasion.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/report-tobacco-or-alcohol-tax-evasion","title":"Report tobacco or alcohol tax evasion","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:17:14+00:00"}]}